| Alias | Purpose | Tech Stack | Domain Skills |
|-------|---------|------------|---------------|
| `ai-platform-webui` | K8s-based AI/ML SaaS platform (GPU orchestration, inference, fine-tuning) | Go (Fiber), React 19, PostgreSQL, NATS, Keycloak, ArgoCD, Kueue | FSD architecture, TDS design system, frontend-expert, backend-expert, e2e-testing |
